latestIgtvVideos.caption:
As mothers, don't we all struggle with saying NO to our children? 

Especially during chaotic mornings before school and work - a bowl of cereal makes for a quick breakfast. But I just have to say NO to sugary cereals no matter how much my children want them! 
I always want to be a YES mom. But the challenge is getting food options so healthy and tasty you can say YES to your kids stress-free. It's heartening to see @slurrpfarm make everything from breakfast cereals to nutritious meals for little ones. All with ZERO maida and no refined sugar, simple goodness of ragi and jowar. With such ingredients, obviously #YesKaTimeAaGaya! 

You can grab their healthy goodies on www.slurrpfarm.com, Amazon, Flipkart, BigBasket and FirstCry.

latestIgtvVideos.title: Mother's day special
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
thank you so much my laddu beta for this wonderful speech😍😍
❤️
❤️ Mother is not just a word, it is the deep emotion, thought and feeling that no other relation can make. 
Mother is a part of God. Mother is a part of Love.
Mother is the heartbeat in the home and without her, there seems to be no heartthrob.
Mother is the name for God in the lips and hearts of little children.
A mother’s work is never done
She works from morning until dawn
She spreads her love
And keeps you warm
But only once a year we say
Mother we wish you “Happy Mothers Day”🙏😘😍
.
.
